{"tid":471694,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"發現家人開始老了","createTime":"2017-11-17T13:39:49.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-20T11:39:00.000Z","uid":126397,"like":88,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"a3f218c72aa742f9150b19701e71401aae329e82","tid":471694,"uid":126397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-17T13:39:49.000Z","msg":"最近屋企人開始帶老花眼鏡  覺得佢地開始老 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n今日同阿爸飲茶 見到佢睇報紙個陣要帶老花眼鏡<br />\n以前細個真係覺得阿爸係好萬能 咩都識 <br />\n但係依家個mon細少少 都睇唔清楚啲字<br />\n<br />\n以前中學要chur DSE 以為考到大學就係報答到佢地<br />\n點知上到大學就要chur GPA 有好多時候都無時間見到佢地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n無發現到原來屋企人開始老...<br />\n真係好驚有一日佢地唔再係身邊 我想像唔到個畫面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8216e53bd34d08564d9888643ba1dea6c7a178a5","tid":471694,"uid":3302,"like":7,"dislike":16,"score":-9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-17T13:42:15.000Z","msg":"放心<br />\n人總有一日會死"},{"pid":"8ee5192ebcc036239adeea4ba4c95b2296cd9baa","tid":471694,"uid":126397,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-17T13:44:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>放心<br />\n人總有一日會死</blockquote><br />\n想像唔到佢地離開我會點樣<br />\n巴打有無試過咁既經歷？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5dd01e40824d23e739a188ac2e28f8b83a7a6aec","tid":471694,"uid":18863,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-17T13:47:03.000Z","msg":"我都試過...有時真係覺得屋企人老緊<br />\n但又唔知可以點做好 仲有好多野未同佢地一齊做<br />\n有好多地方未同佢地一齊去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed314ae025f78f15be4d96ad40c8733731431870","tid":471694,"uid":136901,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-17T13:48:48.000Z","msg":"見到老豆老母越黎越少頭髮<br />\n就不停反思點解細個唔好好孝順佢地  <br />\n以前覺得佢地好煩好噚氣<br />\n但係依家寧願唔去玩都返屋企陪佢地食飯<br />\n唉"},{"pid":"a01ecfa1caa4ba6f022c5a5ebb0a90e302308e54","tid":471694,"uid":126397,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-17T13:51:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>見到老豆老母越黎越少頭髮<br />\n就不停反思點解細個唔好好孝順佢地  <br />\n以前覺得佢地好煩好噚氣<br />\n但係依家寧願唔去玩都返屋企陪佢地食飯<br />\n唉</blockquote><br />\n我都覺 以前讀書個陣 成日叫佢唔好煩<br />\n又覺得佢地管住晒 一啲自由都無<br />\n但近幾年 佢地開始少理我 無好似以前咁成日哦我<br />\n我反而好唔慣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"82f99d225926b7976e54de15febd7016c45998f6","tid":471694,"uid":89595,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-17T13:53:02.000Z","msg":"起碼你仲會同老豆飲茶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71ef52dc67d95d4ce4fc33617ccf037157f6fe69","tid":471694,"uid":126397,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-17T13:54:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我都試過...有時真係覺得屋企人老緊<br />\n但又唔知可以點做好 仲有好多野未同佢地一齊做<br />\n有好多地方未同佢地一齊去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我都有好多野想同佢地做 你會想同佢地做咩呀?<br />\n我仲想同佢地一齊去旅行 有好多好多野想做<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"285d5944cd6cfaf720602a92323709f2516e5f4b","tid":471694,"uid":10330,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-17T13:57:45.000Z","msg":"我都好驚"},{"pid":"5fa5e085430845cf0f34dea69220a60bf6618aeb","tid":471694,"uid":34767,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-17T14:00:53.000Z","msg":"屌 係真係驚既就唔好得個講字<br />\n係度打冇用既<br />\n聽日放假咪同佢地出去玩下唔想出街或者一齊煮下飯囉"},{"pid":"311b404de78172ed3b3cb37e76f8f15d41b9b408","tid":471694,"uid":35087,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-17T14:05:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我都好驚</blockquote><br />\n好想喊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"83628f3929429c803040b547f7d1406ad803819a","tid":471694,"uid":54387,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-17T14:05:46.000Z","msg":"唔只兩老，連我都已經有老花<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c5d99e5bafeaa3444331ec7471344b9dc053085","tid":471694,"uid":126397,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-17T14:08:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>起碼你仲會同老豆飲茶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n而家真係只可以靠呢啲門面功夫扮吓孝順<br />\n但一個禮拜都冇一次 見啲朋友仲多過老豆"},{"pid":"cb3cdf25410eee8af670d8d71a81ebd4f5eb1812","tid":471694,"uid":37493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-17T14:10:49.000Z","msg":"我仲未grad 兩老已經退休<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5dfdb5327ce5a404f90bccf613a9b914f4989eab","tid":471694,"uid":13187,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-17T14:22:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"10ddfc537a586b1fdc53785248be72b58c0c8de2","tid":471694,"uid":100017,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-17T15:13:57.000Z","msg":"老媽子比公司外派左去大陸做野，每星期返香港一次。佢每次返黎都覺得佢老左，好想陪佢地飲茶，但佢同老豆都覺得攰唔想出。<br />\n<br />\n所以依家儲緊錢等我下年可以請兩老去旅行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2fdf36f826095db3e9528286e1cbfde9ea214e9b","tid":471694,"uid":28353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-17T15:23:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  事業仲係一事無成 無法比到野家人 好唔開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a56709299e664769ab1abb3ddee44ed5d5f73666","tid":471694,"uid":18863,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-17T16:37:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我都試過...有時真係覺得屋企人老緊<br />\n但又唔知可以點做好 仲有好多野未同佢地一齊做<br />\n有好多地方未同佢地一齊去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我都有好多野想同佢地做 你會想同佢地做咩呀?<br />\n我仲想同佢地一齊去旅行 有好多好多野想做<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n真係有好多野想做 老豆好鍾意行山<br />\n成日都好想抽時間一家三口去行個山<br />\n然後去飲茶 但係最近老豆對腳有啲問題<br />\n行路開始赤赤痛 我先發現原來再無咩機會可以去做佢地想做既野<br />\n時間唔會忽然間返轉頭 佢地都唔會愈黎愈健康<br />\n有啲時光過左去就係過左去 用幾多錢幾多物質既野都補唔返<br />\n我依家真係好後悔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ed2ea438c7e67abe784ce8f89c8c41f5ca73c51","tid":471694,"uid":151916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-17T16:58:50.000Z","msg":"趁而家多D陪佢地"},{"pid":"c6ffd0c90270a88264f3c0ffd93698346863d580","tid":471694,"uid":126397,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-18T08:24:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>老媽子比公司外派左去大陸做野，每星期返香港一次。佢每次返黎都覺得佢老左，好想陪佢地飲茶，但佢同老豆都覺得攰唔想出。<br />\n<br />\n所以依家儲緊錢等我下年可以請兩老去旅行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n好羨慕啲人可以成日同屋企人去到旅行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n見到好多巴絲都話陪多啲屋企人 但先唔講大家係咪有咁大動力去陪屋企人<br />\n而係現實真係太多限制<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<span style=\"color: pink;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">其實是咪都係藉口</span></span>"},{"pid":"0e169de003505260f7d0236f9dda53268ed93731","tid":471694,"uid":126397,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-18T08:29:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  事業仲係一事無成 無法比到野家人 好唔開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n一直以來努力做好自己 為嘅就係滿足到屋企 將來比到更大嘅幸福屋企人<br />\n但偏偏忽略咗而家<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 到最後乜都畀唔返佢哋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"083caf3f51fc86d8532d2cc0f5c0ca57b190f660","tid":471694,"uid":66943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-18T08:32:26.000Z","msg":"想像唔到自己父母離世個感覺"},{"pid":"8dd9928cfa42c757bda55ab3f4fc792c8aa7af50","tid":471694,"uid":74281,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-18T08:34:50.000Z","msg":"人終需一死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf2f214e2f1c908bc73ea593cb0a6fb534ec819a","tid":471694,"uid":119363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-18T08:35:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>放心<br />\n人總有一日會死</blockquote><br />\n咁點解你唔而家死咗去？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"725e1cb6cffa862bf5d039dffbac89d8ab0816c6","tid":471694,"uid":144529,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-18T08:53:03.000Z","msg":"我雖然都無經歷過 但係有類似既 同我呀爸呀媽同輩既果D舅父都走左<br />\n樓主多D陪屋企人 其實50歲開始已經好危險"}]}